184
00:14:41.208 --> 00:14:42.375
Launch Tube 1 is ready!

185
00:14:42.458 --> 00:14:43.833
Launch Tube 1.

186
00:14:43.916 --> 00:14:44.916
Fire!

187
00:14:47.250 --> 00:14:49.410
-Prepare the decoys!
-Yes. sir! Preparing the decoys!

188
00:14:49.750 --> 00:14:51.375
Enemy torpedo bearing 073!

189
00:14:51.458 --> 00:14:53.500
Contact in 150 seconds!

190
00:14:55.166 --> 00:14:56.333
Decoys are ready!

191
00:14:56.416 --> 00:14:57.416
Launch the decoys!

192
00:15:01.916 --> 00:15:05.416
Ahead 3. down bubble 13 degrees.
Dive to 330 m for emergency evasion.

193
00:15:05.500 --> 00:15:06.500
Yes. sir!

194
00:15:13.625 --> 00:15:15.166
