215
00:16:15.291 --> 00:16:16.875
Seawater density is 1.0372.

216
00:16:16.958 --> 00:16:18.958
Current heading 200 degrees.
speed 1.2 knots.

217
00:16:19.041 --> 00:16:21.481
The sea area conditions
