221
00:16:35.083 --> 00:16:38.666
Lock onto the target
when it leaves the thermocline.

222
00:16:40.083 --> 00:16:41.083
Yes. sir.

223
00:16:46.875 --> 00:16:48.041
380 m.

224
00:16:51.125 --> 00:16:52.250
390 m.

225
00:16:56.000 --> 00:16:57.500
