227
00:17:03.000 --> 00:17:04.000
400 m.

228
00:17:05.875 --> 00:17:07.291
Be ready to fire Launch Tube 2.

229
00:17:13.208 --> 00:17:14.333
Launch Tube 2 is ready.

230
00:17:14.416 --> 00:17:15.625
