232
00:17:40.208 --> 00:17:41.208
Target found!

233
00:17:41.250 --> 00:17:42.625
Bearing 061.

234
00:17:42.708 --> 00:17:43.750
Launch Tube 2. fire!

235
00:17:43.833 --> 00:17:45.083
Firing torpedo.

236
00:17:48.041 --> 00:17:50.500
