238
00:17:55.875 --> 00:17:57.625
Target 1. bearing 058.

239
00:17:57.708 --> 00:17:59.500
Target 2. bearing 065.

240
00:17:59.583 --> 00:18:00.833
It's a self-propelled decoy!

241
00:18:09.250 --> 00:18:10.833
Captain. contact in 30 seconds.

242
00:18:10.916 --> 00:18:12.125
Which one do we hit?

243
00:18:13.458 --> 00:18:15.083
Cao. give me an answer!

244
00:18:25.666 --> 00:18:27.750
COMPOSITE 1

245
00:18:29.458 --> 00:18:30.291
Attack Target 1!

246
00:18:30.375 --> 00:18:31.958
VESSEL 065

247
00:18:35.083 --> 00:18:37.083
No sound of twisting metal was detected.

248
00:18:37.916 --> 00:18:38.750
Damn it!

249
00:18:38.833 --> 00:18:40.333
Be ready to launch Tube 3!

250
00:18:42.791 --> 00:18:46.166
Captain. the decoy's hit.
but that bogey's still on our tail.

251
00:18:46.250 --> 00:18:48.250
Comms. contact the base. Unleash the fury.

252
00:18:48.333 --> 00:18:53.333
-Down bubble 10 degrees. dive to 1.400 ft.
-Down bubble 10 degrees. dive to 1.400 ft.

253
00:18:53.416 --> 00:18:54.250
Aye. sir.

254
00:18:54.333 --> 00:18:56.500
Velocity gradient of sound
